snippet.title: oddheader
snippet.description:
Early 2018 and I've decided to take my stagnant for years, random-upload YouTube channel and transform it into something actually publicly digestible. I envision it as like a hyper audiovisual catalog of various sorts of table topics that you can dive through. Late-night Youtube-stuff for sure. We'll see how it goes.

Interview: 
https://gamingreinvented.com/interview/lets-interview-unused-content-and-video-game-mystery-youtuber-oddheader/
